Sitara's first time on television.. and our first appearance together... couldn't be more special! The non-stop fun, laughter, watching her interact with everyone and dance on stage with such confidence.. was a moment of pride for me!! An absolutely incredible experience.. will remain etched in my memory forever! The contestants are some of the most brilliant dancers I've ever seen and I hope they make the most of this opportunity to inch close to their ultimate dream!! Thank you @zeetelugu for inviting us to the show.. My best wishes to all the participants!! 👍👍

Social distancing is the need of the hour!! It’s a tough call but we need to make it. This is time to sacrifice our social life and prioritize public safety.  Stay indoors as much as you can and make the most of this phase with your family and loved ones. This will keep the virus from spreading and save many lives. 
Ensure you wash your hands frequently and keep your environment clean. Use hand sanitizers as much as possible, use masks only if you think you are sick... Let's continue to follow all the necessary steps until this passes. We are in it together and we will see this through... Let’s beat #COVID19 together🤗🤗🤗 #StaySafe
